						               													<description>Conquista B&amp;iacute;blica is a question and answer game about the Bible. There is a total of 996 questions. The game is for 2 to 6 players, starting at the age they can read.&amp;#10;You roll the dice and navigate over the board. The cell where you land has 6 questions associated. You roll the dice a second time, to determine the number of the question you will have to answer. You may use the Bible to look up your answer. If you answer it correctly, within 30 seconds, you get 3 &amp;ldquo;denarios&amp;rdquo; (coins). If you need the biblical reference, and answer it correctly you only get 1 &amp;ldquo;denario&amp;rdquo;.&amp;#10;When you reach the total of 6 &amp;ldquo;denarios&amp;rdquo;, you may conquer a book. If the cell where you land belongs to a a biblical book, you can pay 6 &amp;ldquo;denarios&amp;rdquo; in order to try to answer correctly 3 questions. If you do so, you conquered the book and receive the corresponding card! The player that conquers the more books wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Original Spanish description:&amp;#10;Conquista B&amp;iacute;blica &amp;eacute; um jogo de perguntas e respostas sobre a B&amp;iacute;blia. Perguntas sobre reis, profetas, sacerdotes, homens e mulheres, na&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, cidades, ap&amp;oacute;stolos, alimentos, armas, habita&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, batalhas, viagens, etc, ir&amp;atilde;o testar os seus conhecimentos e ajud&amp;aacute;-lo a conhecer melhor a Palavra de Deus.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
